    oneSentenceSummary: "The University of Denver combines private-school access, strong alumni connectivity, business and law prestige, outdoor-industry proximity, and Denver's rapidly expanding economy to create one of the strongest relationship-driven career platforms in the Mountain West.",

    pipeline: "Founded in 1864 and located in Denver. DU is a private research university known for business, law, international studies, psychology, hospitality, real estate, public policy, and entrepreneurship. Its location places students directly inside one of America's fastest-growing metropolitan economies, providing unusually strong internship and professional networking access throughout college.",

