      transferNotes: "UCCS accepts transfers broadly through Colorado's statewide articulation system. Pikes Peak State College is the primary local feeder. Given UCCS's high freshman acceptance rate, the CC pathway is primarily a cost-savings mechanism. Cybersecurity and engineering programs have specific prerequisite requirements."
