    archetype: "Environmental Leadership & Social Innovation College",

    oneSentenceSummary: "Prescott College is a highly experiential, mission-driven institution that develops environmental leaders, outdoor educators, nonprofit founders, sustainability professionals, and social entrepreneurs through one of the most student-directed educational models in America.",

    pipeline: "Founded in 1966 during the height of educational experimentation and environmental awareness movements, Prescott College has built a national reputation for experiential education, environmental studies, adventure education, sustainability, social justice, and community leadership. The college attracts students seeking purpose-driven careers and lifestyles rather than conventional prestige pathways.",

