    geographicInfluenceRadius: "California dominant — Silicon Valley and SoCal aerospace corridor; national reach in architecture; Central Coast wine and agriculture industry",

    economicOutcome: "Exceptional in California engineering and architecture — the most reliable undergraduate engineering pipeline into California's technology and aerospace sector outside of Berkeley; strong in agriculture, business, and environmental management; alumni network in California engineering is among the most active referral cultures in the state",

