    geographicInfluenceRadius: "DFW Metroplex dominant; national in jazz and music education; Texas statewide in business and logistics; growing film industry pipeline through Texas production expansion",

    economicOutcome: "Dominant in jazz and music education nationally; strong in supply chain and logistics (DFW freight ecosystem), business and accounting, journalism and communications, fashion merchandising, and film; DFW Fortune 500 corridor creates broad professional placement for business and engineering graduates",

    gradCities: ["Dallas", "Fort Worth", "Denton", "Austin", "Houston", "Nashville", "Los Angeles"],

